{"product_id":"madara-glycolic-glow-toner-150ml","title":"MÁDARA Glycolic Glow Toner 150ml","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003eExperience visible skin renewal with this glycolic acid toner — a gentle liquid formula that exfoliates, smooths and brightens the look of skin. Powered by 5% Glycolic Acid and Juniper Stem Cells, it removes dead surface cells and targets areas of pigmentation, revealing a more luminous complexion and an even-looking skin tone. Infused with advanced, clinically studied exosomes, it enhances the delivery of apple extract where your skin needs it most to let you achieve refined appearance and a healthy-looking glow.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eApply to cleansed skin every morning and\/or evening. Pat onto face with hands or use a cotton pad.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"\u003ePerform a patch test on a small area before use. This formula contains AHAs, which can increase your skin’s sensitivity to the sun and the risk of sunburn. Always apply sunscreen, wear protective clothing and limit sun exposure while using this toner.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eAQUA; GLYCOLIC ACID; GLYCERIN; POTASSIUM HYDROXIDE; SODIUM PCA; SODIUM LEVULINATE; PHENETHYL ALCOHOL; PYRUS MALUS (APPLE) FRUIT EXTRACT; SODIUM BENZOATE; PHOSPHOLIPIDS; LACTOBACILLUS FERMENT; HYDROLYZED HYALURONIC ACID; SODIUM HYALURONATE; JUNIPERUS COMMUNIS (JUNIPER) CALLUS EXTRACT\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"productPage-ingredientMessage-3FP\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"richContent-root-3Sy\"\u003e* Please note that ingredient lists may change and slightly vary from time to time. You will always find the most up-to-date information on the actual product packaging.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"MADARA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":53351776878919,"sku":null,"price":29.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/madara-glycolic-glow-toner-150ml-6984978.jpg?v=1771463673","url":"https:\/\/bioskina.com\/products\/madara-glycolic-glow-toner-150ml","provider":"bioskina","version":"1.0","type":"link"}